{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_01","textHome":"啊，那个……我是夏目佳子！很喜欢看书……@无论何时何地都会看书！只要是有趣的我都@会看！昨天看了本推理小说，标题是「 弗氏@飞鼠杀人事件」！我很推荐，还请你一定要@看看！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_18","textHome":"……啊！这里是……现实对吧！？我，看书看得@太入迷了，感觉就像进入了故事中一样……@真的如同身临其境……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_19","textHome":"真没想到我竟然能做到这一步……@我也吓了一跳！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_20","textHome":"说不定，我……可能领悟了什么！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_21","textHome":"实际上我自己也在写小说。虽然只写了一半，@但一直没有停笔。不过读和写差距很大……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_22","textHome":"听我说！我写好了！小说！虽然只是短篇小@说，但是是完成了的！一开始写起来好苦恼，@后半段就一气呵成了。这就是所谓的「浑然@忘我」的状态吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_23","textHome":"我将来的梦想，就是继承夏目书房，然后作为@作家出道！……要是能这样就好了……但哪会@这么顺利呢？这个梦要是能做下去就好了~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_24","textHome":"能够再次相会比什么都重要！就像是从夹着@书签的那一页，继续开始阅读一样！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_25","textHome":"……早上好……嗯……我马上起床……@不好意思，我早上有些醒不过来……@哈啊~……能让我再睡会儿吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_26","textHome":"这家的拉面，很好吃哦！那我要大碗卤蛋@拉面，面硬一些油少一些！@……啊，葱不够可以再添吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3011_00_27","textHome":"我平常顺道去会去车站附近的书店，今天就@直接回家……嗯？莫非今天是新刊发售……@那，那还是去看看吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":301100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json"